title: Infant mortality rate in the Philippines 2018
summary: In general Deaths per 1,000 live births has fallen over the Year.
Deaths per 1,000 live births is slightly decreasing from 2008 to 2014.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2009 and 2010.
The highest Deaths per 1,000 live births, of value 25.5 was reached at Year 2008
The lowest Deaths per 1,000 live births, of value 24.0 was reported at Year 2014
